data.description:
(Sellers concessions available) Fabulous 2020 built corner lot home in the lovely community of Hasting's Farms! This Lennar Next-Gen, is a true gem with it's own casita! Imagine the possibilities! The casita features a full kitchen, separate front entry, it's own single car garage, laundry, bedroom, bathroom and side yard door. This design offers lots of extra privacy and ease of coming and going for guests or a multi-generational living arrangement.  If you enjoy splashing around or relaxing by the pool, you're in luck because this home boasts a brand new pool and spa, perfect for those hot AZ summers and those brisk winter evenings!
The main home offers an upgraded gourmet kitchen with upgraded appliances, large walk in pantry and ample counter space. There is plenty of room for the whole family with the large open floorplan and 3 spacious bedrooms offered in the marin home! The delightful, family-friendly community of Hasting's Farms is located just minutes from restaurants, shops, botanical gardens, lots of multi-use trails, San Tan Mountain park,  Schnepff Farns, the 24 and 202 freeways and lots more. But why leave the neighborhood when plenty of fun, family friendly things are hosted right inside the community!
